author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
DOOM: The Dark Ages | Hugo Martin's Game Director Playthrough - Ch. 19 Horde Mode Gaming's Ripatorium 2.0 setup Arachnophobia + Saleem's WIP blockout for a DOOM Eternal Mod: Codename Corrosive!

Join us as DOOM: The Dark Ages' Game Director Hugo Martin does his first playthrough of Horde Mode Gaming's Combat Encounter setup and playtests Saleem's DOOM Eternal WIP blockout mod while providing his unique insights into the game’s design.

Here's Horde Mode Gaming's Ripatorium 2.0 Combat Setup: ARACHNOPHOBIA  
(Recommending a thirteen minute timer)
Wave One - G4G100000H101
Wave Two - GGG10G10012001
Wave Three (Repeat Once) - 0GG122000H204
Wave Four - 0GG10GG00H00G2
Wave Five - 4MG92G00113A0008

For more information on all things DOOM: The Dark Ages and id Software, follow these channels and join the Slayers Club.

author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
Progress through a new scoreboard in Season 23: Blood x Rust to earn new rewards that channel your inner raider or deathclaw and even uncover some treasures from New Vegas that have made their way to Appalachia.

Season 23 launches December 2 with the Fallout 76: Burning Springs update.
